article.headline: Utah Valley St. 64, Texas-Pan American 42
article.story: OREM, Utah -- Jordan Swarbrick scored 16 points, and Utah Valley thumped Texas-Pan American 64-42 on Saturday night. Swarbrick was one of three Wolverines (15-10, 7-1 Great West) to score in double figures. Ben Aird had 14 and Isiah Williams scored 13. Brandon Provost led the Broncs (4-22, 1-8 Great West) with 15 points. Utah Valley opened the game with a 19-7 run and led 31-21 at the half. The final margin of 22 points was the largest of the game for the Wolverines.
